{"tid":2186284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（責任全在...）邊境偷襲戰印度士兵陣亡  華春瑩：他們是被自己軍車砸死的","createTime":"2020-09-03T00:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T04:01:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcf1846874fcd0afeab5e626b4ab7d051c1c3b6","tid":2186284,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"中國及印度軍隊在今年6月15日，於邊界加勒萬河谷（Galwan River）爆發衝突，當時造成20名印度士兵身亡，導致兩國仇視感升溫。近日「中印衝突」再起，印度更爆出有一名西藏裔士兵遭解放軍打死，對此，中國外交部發言人華春瑩就表示，她不知道消息從何而來，但她看了外媒的報導，認為印度士兵是遭自己的軍車砸死的，與中國無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=807953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D807953&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=81c51b36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D807953&h=18107359\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=807953</a>"},{"pid":"8cea4f1570710658c85c512833fec189c337ed29","tid":2186284,"uid":18241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T00:58:36.000Z","msg":"有得攞彩又縮...？"},{"pid":"1d6a06749ec56f9e0effef24e7f93d974e5e38ee","tid":2186284,"uid":176313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T00:58:46.000Z","msg":"翻譯俾印度睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e088cc70a27c1d7bb636ae55f38dc3f257b6c76","tid":2186284,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40a3f138e842979b1c3b2d10006a3958c53547c5","tid":2186284,"uid":4285,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T01:00:12.000Z","msg":"華大媽真係撥火高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d90c38e8988b24910718f700a14077de1efd140","tid":2186284,"uid":77968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTi